data.description: Welcome to a well maintained 2-bed, 1.75-bath home in Highland Knolls, featuring a circular driveway, potential for small RV/trailer parking, newer windows, newer HVAC, and much more! Inside the home, you'll find the open kitchen/dining area that comes with modern wood-like flooring, white cabinetry, white appliances, and the dining area has a custom light fixture. The large living area is equipped with a brick fireplace and a doggy door leading to the backyard. Both bedrooms have large closets and the master bedroom comes with a ceiling fan. The two restrooms boast large vanity mirrors, plenty of storage space, and the master has a step-in shower. Stepping into the backyard, you will fall in love with the extended covered patio, a large grass area, and partial block wall fencing.
